---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy | Miles Sowden"
  description="How this site handles your privacy. No cookies, no tracking, no personal data."
>
  <section class="pt-48 pb-32 max-md:pt-32 max-md:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <h1 class="font-display text-[3.5rem] max-lg:text-5xl max-md:text-[2.5rem] leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-text-primary mb-10">
        Privacy
      </h1>

      <div class="max-w-[720px] space-y-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3">The short version</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            This site does not use cookies, does not track individual visitors and does not collect personal information. There are no sign-ups, no contact forms and no analytics that identify you.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3">Analytics</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            This site uses Cloudflare Web Analytics to understand aggregate visitor patterns. It does not use cookies, does not track individual users and does not collect personal information. It is privacy-first by design.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div id="fit-finder">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3">Fit Finder</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            The Fit Finder at <a href="/fit" class="text-text-accent hover:underline">/fit</a> accepts a role description as an uploaded PDF or pasted text. Your document is not stored on this site's servers. It is held in memory only for the duration of the request and then discarded.
          </p>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mt-8 mb-3">Data in transit</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            The text from your document is sent over an encrypted connection (HTTPS) to Anthropic's Claude API for analysis. This is a third-party AI service. You should assume that commercially sensitive or confidential role descriptions travel through Anthropic's infrastructure.
          </p>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mt-8 mb-3">Anthropic's data handling</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            This site uses Anthropic's commercial API. Under Anthropic's commercial terms, API inputs are <strong class="text-text-primary">not used to train models</strong>. Anthropic retains API logs for up to 30 days for trust and safety purposes, after which they are automatically deleted. For full details, see <a href="https://privacy.claude.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-text-accent hover:underline">Anthropic's privacy centre</a>.
          </p>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mt-8 mb-3">What this site stores</h3>
          <ul class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary space-y-2 list-disc pl-6">
            <li>Your IP address and a request count are stored for 24 hours to prevent abuse. No document content is included.</li>
            <li>A notification containing the role title only (not the document) is sent to a private channel for usage monitoring.</li>
            <li>No user accounts, email addresses or personal details are collected.</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mt-8 mb-3">Shared result links</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            If you share a result link, the analysis is encoded in the URL itself using a signed token. No server stores the results. Links expire after 30 days.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3">External services</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            Google Fonts are loaded from Google servers to display typography on this site. Google may log standard server access information for these requests.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3">Security</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            All connections to this site are encrypted. The site enforces strict security policies so that content can only be loaded from trusted sources. A board chair on hotel wifi and a recruiter on a train both get the same protection.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3">Third-party links</h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            This site links to LinkedIn and WhatsApp. When you follow those links, you leave this site and are subject to those platforms' privacy policies.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
